==Purpose==
This template gives an [[equation]] passed in as [[M:Help:Template|numbered parameter]] <nowiki>{{{1}}} a number {{{2}}}</nowiki>, which is displayed in the far right column. This also creates an anchor (<nowiki>#equation-{{{2}}}</nowiki>), which can be adjusted with the <code>id</code> parameter.

==Usage==
<pre>
{{Equation|1=e=m c^2\,|2=1}}
{{Equation|1=a^2+b^2=c^2\,|2=2}}
{{Equation|1=X(t)= V_0 * t + A*t^2\,|2=3}}
</pre>
results in:
{{Equation|1=e=m c^2\,|2=1}}
{{Equation|1=a^2+b^2=c^2\,|2=2}}
{{Equation|1=X(t)= V_0 * t + A*t^2\,|2=3}}

:Note: Wikisyntax (e.g. formatting templates like {{tlxw|sub}}) won't work in this template, use [[LaTeX]] syntax instead.
